                        <summary>A copper plate issued in the Jovian cycle year <foreign>kaṟā</foreign> (that is, <foreign>kara</foreign>) during the reign of Tirumalai Nāyaka, that is, precisely June 18, 1651. Records a royal order bestowing <foreign>nāṭṭāmai</foreign> and <foreign>māṉipam</foreign> to Veṅkiṭṭi Nākkaṉ.</summary>
